{"tid":328462,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"神戶除左姬路城，重有邊d景點要去？","createTime":"2017-07-19T14:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T11:53:39.000Z","uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae43095942faf0142a292f6c57416585601eb6e5","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"距離有馬遠唔遠？<br />\n需要住一兩晚嗎？<br />\n<br />\n毒撚出城，唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc1e5467488147f6020bc183632b1ff4f61d7db","tid":328462,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"700d31086d4d41861ced586cc5609425d36f3116","tid":328462,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:01:52.000Z","msg":"有馬浸個温泉 點都要留一日啦"},{"pid":"1460d2632add3aebf3c90a9019ad06a0ac5258df","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>杯麵博物館</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪係三宮站?"},{"pid":"099f261924908e54799625cd2df8f7699cf81110","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有馬浸個温泉 點都要留一日啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有馬離姬路遠唔遠？還是近三宮站?"},{"pid":"7317a9d0b06af7ff9aa1e715351df455a7b74d9f","tid":328462,"uid":56483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有馬浸個温泉 點都要留一日啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有馬離姬路遠唔遠？還是近三宮站?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/maps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fmaps&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2eca5ae9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/maps</a>"},{"pid":"11f8b4192e860b9d0492831a41ecc577cf20840b","tid":328462,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:31:30.000Z","msg":"早幾日去完異人館<br />\n條上斜行到pk"},{"pid":"1e56cc8c13fedeba47d6229f7bf3d810de7e1b6e","tid":328462,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"LM 下年可能去神戶"},{"pid":"56fbd451993e9668835fb93d7bc83ffa7b38f577","tid":328462,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日去完異人館<br />\n條上斜行到pk</blockquote><br />\n異人館伏到 <br />\n行餐死得個睇字"},{"pid":"30934eece49634079215eedbdc1683c2e240ced6","tid":328462,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"6月去完黎 一日內先係神戶去姫路 再番神戶食牛 再去浸溫泉 再番神戶拎行李再去京都 攰撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a866fab50c8e4c90ee9643d849872f2882d52b","tid":328462,"uid":70553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"嚴格黎講基佬城唔算神戶  係神戶搭鐵都仲要8 9個字先到<br />\n<br />\n神戶主要係上六甲摩耶山睇夜景  日頭就去下食神戶牛<br />\n<br />\n以上行程都肯定用上一日時間  所以去有馬的話就肯定加多半日先"},{"pid":"c8424d029bb9519e73d2fbd47f7672a90d31cec7","tid":328462,"uid":59777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"姬路城 <br />\n係姬路<br />\n唔係神戶.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40f2b13a2bb2776b4b49d153c8c1009f9e18844","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LM 下年可能去神戶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58f1e742e3f1322f888967dcead304728df64ef","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日去完異人館<br />\n條上斜行到pk</blockquote><br />\n好無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd2ebc165caa50d2657f9b908f8181996ec7615","tid":328462,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9n3p0cfm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9n3p0cfm&h=2a3e5bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zygfea5o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzygfea5o&h=dc138c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基佬城真係一生人一定要去一次，超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33af42c13699990f25993bc1b4cd4a24aac50b64","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6月去完黎 一日內先係神戶去姫路 再番神戶食牛 再去浸溫泉 再番神戶拎行李再去京都 攰撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一日？唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece33e86485d37b0fdd5d085e63f93870d0c5064","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚴格黎講基佬城唔算神戶  係神戶搭鐵都仲要8 9個字先到<br />\n<br />\n神戶主要係上六甲摩耶山睇夜景  日頭就去下食神戶牛<br />\n<br />\n以上行程都肯定用上一日時間  所以去有馬的話就肯定加多半日先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果去姬路城又去有馬，最後回到京都，咁應該係邊度住?"},{"pid":"8e91b718c83c00d58598b31ad28fe29dae85039e","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:30:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姬路城 <br />\n係姬路<br />\n唔係神戶.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白了，是姬路站。"},{"pid":"745126ef19d5b75a6998a94444d1ac5573fdcac6","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/9n3p0cfm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9n3p0cfm&h=2a3e5bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zygfea5o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzygfea5o&h=dc138c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基佬城真係一生人一定要去一次，超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好靚，一定去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144336fefcea7504d2eeec056474e3c22eae3019","tid":328462,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"基婆城"},{"pid":"96b01c08cab50f0f41e258a5493cf083cbc87d01","tid":328462,"uid":74575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/9n3p0cfm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9n3p0cfm&h=2a3e5bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zygfea5o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzygfea5o&h=dc138c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基佬城真係一生人一定要去一次，超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n燈柱阻尻住！"},{"pid":"e7fd83dddba05494e82b894861edfbb9979ff28c","tid":328462,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"巴打望下地圖先開post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8d3afe3dcd30ff166532a08282a9fa2bb4e339","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打望下地圖先開post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係唔識先問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37d8ca292410f3a9544d91e228a918c7aaf53b5","tid":328462,"uid":74897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T21:49:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打望下地圖先開post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係唔識先問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伸手到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ed3af8c043e316f0b80965d005f61752119c31","tid":328462,"uid":6366,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打望下地圖先開post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係唔識先問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伸手到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學雞地圖/車程又都唔識睇學人自由行？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真姬路玩唔到一日 通常早上玩完會坐多程車去東京果邊<br />\n夜晚再坐返同一條線返大阪酒店"},{"pid":"39f3fa4d04cab3b8b31087878003044cc56926b4","tid":328462,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:33:55.000Z","msg":"如果有女一齊去就建議神戶公園前酒店住返晚。個海景露台好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再座下摩天輪，睇音樂噴泉，食埋個神戶牛，條女仲唔手到拿來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(個人覺得神戶公園個邊夜晚真係好鬼浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚就算吧啦，一對對，閃到盲"},{"pid":"60055956c246fc9eef08f584dfa1543271f39017","tid":328462,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>距離有馬遠唔遠？<br />\n需要住一兩晚嗎？<br />\n<br />\n毒撚出城，唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有馬唔遠，搭鐵路印象中唔使一個鐘，溫泉你都浸唔到好耐㗎啦，最多咪一兩位鐘，再喺附近行下，一個下晝就可以搞掂返神戶，跟手去睇埋摩耶山夜景"},{"pid":"c00f8767c082b1153814189bd27935e811653148","tid":328462,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T22:56:33.000Z","msg":"異人館"},{"pid":"34481a293c9f46bcd8ef2ea41b754af5304ae8ed","tid":328462,"uid":35586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:44:36.000Z","msg":"摩耶山"},{"pid":"293eea83223344c2285d4bfab5b90dd17ba6ccc5","tid":328462,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:48:09.000Z","msg":"姬路城正，上年去用咗我大半日行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbf93be9d2bd1fd409894bf05c22aa22b75bc6d","tid":328462,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T23:53:19.000Z","msg":"姬路城果頭都算係神戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf561c3b423f848ad38be2e4706bc5eb8f5f223a","tid":328462,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾日去完異人館<br />\n條上斜行到pk</blockquote><br />\n好無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全部都要俾錢先入得<br />\n3000円行到主要果8個館 另外3個再加1400(好似係)<br />\n3連休中間果日去 多人到pk<br />\n係新神戶落車仲要行上去<br />\n<br />\n涼少少去應該幾舒服<br />\n<br />\n11-12點左右去到三宮食牛&gt;下晝異人館&gt;夜晚神戶港咁玩應該幾好"},{"pid":"25dbdfb864cd0d5fe95348ee0cf9489a4b1ab900","tid":328462,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:39:33.000Z","msg":"我個陣係 姬路城&gt;神戶&gt;有馬 一日遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n神戶只係試下神戶牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b3c0a047069ccb34e41db908564b0fb687fbec","tid":328462,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:40:15.000Z","msg":"神戶垃圾地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c590adec672be37d5a46ebee2f3015152e48ef","tid":328462,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:41:53.000Z","msg":"姬路城2年前開返果陣去過<br />\n好多人<br />\n就係去排隊行樓梯<br />\n唔似其他城咁有文物展覽睇 好似係<br />\n<br />\n如果想去同姬路城合照 可以去好古園<br />\n果度望到姬路城"},{"pid":"3586c94508e4c4fc2fcbb1126a0e1aecb1901267","tid":328462,"uid":799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/084303_6a8d06a703ab8c09147145c85b786cca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F084303_6a8d06a703ab8c09147145c85b786cca.jpg&h=a7239211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幾靚既"},{"pid":"1e06193b0a265ecad034fcc3ea674b0badceda87","tid":328462,"uid":70553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嚴格黎講基佬城唔算神戶  係神戶搭鐵都仲要8 9個字先到<br />\n<br />\n神戶主要係上六甲摩耶山睇夜景  日頭就去下食神戶牛<br />\n<br />\n以上行程都肯定用上一日時間  所以去有馬的話就肯定加多半日先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果去姬路城又去有馬，最後回到京都，咁應該係邊度住?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你一早去左基佬城先  中午番神戶食飯<br />\n<br />\n飯後上六甲摩耶山再搭埋cable car過有馬<br />\n<br />\n浸到咁上下就番上山睇夜景  之後番酒店<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過京都好L遠喎  你會唔會認真睇下地圖先呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6967e6345f6a9a4a4d98ade84615e969e4a1e6a5","tid":328462,"uid":34748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:49:42.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"13d3d45d321995121c79e96cc4794718123c4b2f","tid":328462,"uid":2028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾日去完異人館<br />\n條上斜行到pk</blockquote><br />\n異人館伏到 <br />\n行餐死得個睇字</blockquote><br />\n入場費仲要好撚貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31484e9710c73f4168680c0d29717bd858396a96","tid":328462,"uid":9647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085456_4ab6748368e514d0aae02116f4a46bb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085456_4ab6748368e514d0aae02116f4a46bb8.jpg&h=9fdd6dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085501_b4e235b4e93a44b94dac99af71a24e39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085501_b4e235b4e93a44b94dac99af71a24e39.jpg&h=09cc2fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085508_6c9dd2ee95412a3c0f621b55f7ae5a66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085508_6c9dd2ee95412a3c0f621b55f7ae5a66.jpg&h=d97567f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基佬城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981f558794bc5bfb817b52c0deb3d904d4481fe2","tid":328462,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:01:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085456_4ab6748368e514d0aae02116f4a46bb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085456_4ab6748368e514d0aae02116f4a46bb8.jpg&h=9fdd6dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085501_b4e235b4e93a44b94dac99af71a24e39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085501_b4e235b4e93a44b94dac99af71a24e39.jpg&h=09cc2fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085508_6c9dd2ee95412a3c0f621b55f7ae5a66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085508_6c9dd2ee95412a3c0f621b55f7ae5a66.jpg&h=d97567f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基佬城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好靚呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想去"},{"pid":"e2d6fc79d197c5e090d7921811024bfcdb555659","tid":328462,"uid":51323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:08:54.000Z","msg":"羽柴秀吉"},{"pid":"ffb99c860084d4a761febde82712193dda0f950a","tid":328462,"uid":41965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姬路城2年前開返果陣去過<br />\n好多人<br />\n就係去排隊行樓梯<br />\n唔似其他城咁有文物展覽睇 好似係<br />\n<br />\n如果想去同姬路城合照 可以去好古園<br />\n果度望到姬路城</blockquote><br />\n個城同天守本身咪係文物囉"},{"pid":"6208bdd5004556351e4f9ba5b861029c543e8bbe","tid":328462,"uid":12083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"上個乜乜花園 幾靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/100148_1acd3acf7f895f3925524f2b20bd604d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F100148_1acd3acf7f895f3925524f2b20bd604d.jpg&h=56f90f7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0257113c6ba0ddf095b475bb1e0dc56700f0d4f","tid":328462,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"神戶港真係冇乜好睇，見過維港就不覺得不外如是，上海外灘仲好睇過佢"},{"pid":"f7d6335a79f4a06226e4a1ec43d722576809dc49","tid":328462,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"似乎神戶除左食牛都冇乜好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8778ebacab9ea1ff9c6b4bb61eb42f88ee19304","tid":328462,"uid":9647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似乎神戶除左食牛都冇乜好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次諗住神戶食牛  結果去完姬路直上有馬skip左神戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5819a0fb5002c4a8e4ce353223bb713bf289a0f0","tid":328462,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>姬路城2年前開返果陣去過<br />\n好多人<br />\n就係去排隊行樓梯<br />\n唔似其他城咁有文物展覽睇 好似係<br />\n<br />\n如果想去同姬路城合照 可以去好古園<br />\n果度望到姬路城</blockquote><br />\n個城同天守本身咪係文物囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝閣下提供有用資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395dee562e1efed38f14757c24938330d84e20c4","tid":328462,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"我去神戶係為左睇球星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428d256d3b440cecc11641f2e0efdaa5f8147f19","tid":328462,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"神戶可以唔洗去<br />\n直接去姬路城"},{"pid":"b124b69f96147d84542f028559bbea51e60b370d","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打望下地圖先開post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係唔識先問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伸手到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學雞地圖/車程又都唔識睇學人自由行？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真姬路玩唔到一日 通常早上玩完會坐多程車去東京果邊<br />\n夜晚再坐返同一條線返大阪酒店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a6b805cf603203a289b2fd46597d8077261372","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果有女一齊去就建議神戶公園前酒店住返晚。個海景露台好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再座下摩天輪，睇音樂噴泉，食埋個神戶牛，條女仲唔手到拿來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(個人覺得神戶公園個邊夜晚真係好鬼浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚就算吧啦，一對對，閃到盲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實好撚貴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3d67b05c79f7de98835e7b3a5fa5de03a6e54e","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姬路城果頭都算係神戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姬路，<br />\n<br />\n兵庫縣先係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a8874a88c614776b12ce790c368adc164fd014","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個陣係 姬路城&gt;神戶&gt;有馬 一日遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n神戶只係試下神戶牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一日票？"},{"pid":"36d929724df1cd67d6ae244fd2bffa7823061643","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神戶垃圾地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人都咁講，但順道去姬路同有馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8678eb044d932a58d2e4ebd18acfca9d1afbf858","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/084303_6a8d06a703ab8c09147145c85b786cca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F084303_6a8d06a703ab8c09147145c85b786cca.jpg&h=a7239211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幾靚既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ec56ce37c5004e5d655dc650998defa1aa2654","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嚴格黎講基佬城唔算神戶  係神戶搭鐵都仲要8 9個字先到<br />\n<br />\n神戶主要係上六甲摩耶山睇夜景  日頭就去下食神戶牛<br />\n<br />\n以上行程都肯定用上一日時間  所以去有馬的話就肯定加多半日先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果去姬路城又去有馬，最後回到京都，咁應該係邊度住?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你一早去左基佬城先  中午番神戶食飯<br />\n<br />\n飯後上六甲摩耶山再搭埋cable car過有馬<br />\n<br />\n浸到咁上下就番上山睇夜景  之後番酒店<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過京都好L遠喎  你會唔會認真睇下地圖先呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有睇圖，所以先諗住係神戶住一晚。"},{"pid":"7212aae25d4b604df84dd0b4a43771435390142c","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085456_4ab6748368e514d0aae02116f4a46bb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085456_4ab6748368e514d0aae02116f4a46bb8.jpg&h=9fdd6dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085501_b4e235b4e93a44b94dac99af71a24e39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085501_b4e235b4e93a44b94dac99af71a24e39.jpg&h=09cc2fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085508_6c9dd2ee95412a3c0f621b55f7ae5a66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085508_6c9dd2ee95412a3c0f621b55f7ae5a66.jpg&h=d97567f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基佬城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩有櫻花睇，巴打三月尾去?"},{"pid":"e7df03c54a0155217798513f3709a757c6de1b48","tid":328462,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日去完異人館<br />\n條上斜行到pk</blockquote><br />\n果到真係唔係情侶去黎把撚<br />\n上次三條麻甩佬去左, 其中一個黑左面"},{"pid":"230f1afcdc7e349ded7e152257d1745dd3e9fac1","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似乎神戶除左食牛都冇乜好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊間介紹，個個都話m字頭個間百年老店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e0078aeea8e53489cfbb3a498c2ec4bfa424ef","tid":328462,"uid":9120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:45:47.000Z","msg