/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我曾經係明治神宮hea左成個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前去神宮就係貪佢寧靜，係度hea下諗下野，近年都好難囉，記得有次係某神宮正在享受緊個寧靜，有班強國撚剎到，屌佢老母嘈撚到呢，，，即刻迫住要走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647d0a83dbf7079cd95cfa623b0d8b710f31e6be","tid":328462,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去神户港灣塔間星巴克hea<br />\n我試過冇野做坐草地成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實去旅行太趕真係好辛苦，有時hea下先係享受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 你有時間可以去<br />\n坐草地吹下海風好舒服 <br />\n又多日本妹望</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去歐洲坐海灘睇鬼妹先係人生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5327868e6675c7b34e0ae371692fd4fbb99a5b","tid":328462,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"有馬"},{"pid":"6281a61eb7e0eb0dbcb8361c93f1ba049dbd35e8","tid":328462,"uid":9647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:37:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085456_4ab6748368e514d0aae02116f4a46bb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085456_4ab6748368e514d0aae02116f4a46bb8.jpg&h=9fdd6dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085501_b4e235b4e93a44b94dac99af71a24e39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F085501_b4e235b4e93a44b94dac99af71a24e39.jpg&h=09cc2fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/085508_6c9dd2ee95412a3c0f621b55f7ae5a66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A